Carefree of Colorado was established in 1971 after introducing the first
truly automatic roll up awning for Recreational Vehicles. Since then,
our unique focus has been on the design, development, manufacture and
development of RV Awnings and related accessories. Carefree is the only
full-line awning and accessories maker for recreational vehicles
worldwide. Carefree offers the most comprehensive and cutting-edge
solutions for vertical/lateral arm, box, slide-out, window, and entry
door awnings available for use in entertainment, residential, and
industrial applications.

Carefree has had millions of awnings installed worldwide on every sort
of RV and specialized vehicle imaginable. Any awning ... anywhere!
